Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.94,0:00:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到阿富汗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Welcome to Afghanistan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是安琪拉亚当斯\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is Angela Adams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是联邦调查局的探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm a special agent with the Federal Bureau of Investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.62,0:00:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲是法拉兹哈姆札\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your father is Faraz Hamzad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.25,0:00:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字是帕瓦娜\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Your name is Parwana.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.63,0:00:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们听说你不介意给哈姆札制造麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We were told that causing Hamzad trouble wouldn't be a problem for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.21,0:00:30.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会给他带来什么麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What kind of trouble will this cause him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.93,0:00:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毁灭性的麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The devastating kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.59,0:00:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梅西巴哈矿床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Meshbahar Deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法拉兹哈姆札发现了它 打算开采矿床\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Faraz Hamzad found it. He has plans to exploit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.31,0:00:42.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正在看 一切都停止了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am looking at it as we speak. Everything is stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里有塔利班的士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There are Talib soldiers here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.52,0:00:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是来找哈姆札的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am here for Hamzad.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.94,0:00:49.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不必听你的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He does not answer to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.11,0:00:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要叫他出来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Will you be producing him,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.36,0:00:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我来带走他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or will I be coming to take him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.16,0:00:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里已经不安全了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not safe for you here anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.28,0:00:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要去哪里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.37,0:00:59.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个我告诉过你母亲的洞穴\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A cave that I once told your mother of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的藏身处 让她消声匿迹\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A place she could hide. Disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\bord0\fs18\b1}《亡命再劫》\N第二季第三集
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.10,0:01:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs21}本WEB版外挂字幕由  {\c&H9B30FF&}风吹来的那片云{\c&HFFFFFF&}  双语合并
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.32,0:04:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安琪拉 别太用力抱他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Angela… just be careful with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么事了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么深入这里并不容易\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It wasn't easy getting this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是怎么来的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How'd you even get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.97,0:04:40.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛莉安\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Marion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.22,0:04:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她让我们进来也会救我们出去 一通电话就能让直升机来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}She got us in. She'll get us out. The chopper is just a phone call away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.85,0:04:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该回家了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time to go home now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.58,0:05:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果把他留在这里 他会死的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we leave him here, he'll die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们不会这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, we're not going to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.64,0:05:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 听着…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay. Listen--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有很多事要谈 但是一定要送他回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We have a lot to talk about, but we have to get him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要他 他一个人是回不去的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need him there, and he's not going to make it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家的人也需要我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm needed home too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.61,0:05:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他和他做的事 你是知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Because of him. Because of what he did. I know you know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.57,0:05:43.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你不要来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you not to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:51.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你照顾雪若和亨利 别管我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you to look after Cheryl and Henry, and not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Em.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.37,0:05:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小艾 他是因为疼爱你才会来这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Em, he came here only because he loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.50,0:05:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才发生的事则是为了保护我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And what happened just now, that was to protect me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:05:59.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他知道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Does he know?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:10.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你告诉他我的身份了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you tell him what I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.40,0:06:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你们就应该不难理解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Well, then this shouldn't be hard for either of you to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.28,0:06:24.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能把他丢在这里等死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't leave him here to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:27.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要请你们帮我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm asking you to help me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是时候了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.54,0:06:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's time for you to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都很清楚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We both know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我不能在你受重伤时离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No, not like this. Not with you like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你必须走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,官兵正在他家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's government soldiers in his house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:52.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们虽然是去找他 但主要是为了我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They've come for him, but they're there because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:54.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在找的人是我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're looking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.81,0:06:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那一家人和那里的所有人都有危险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The family, everyone there, they're in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.02,0:06:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们需要他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They need him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要带他回去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I'm going to get him back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们会帮我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you going to help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.33,0:07:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 搞什么鬼\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Excuse me, but what the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.22,0:07:31.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-什么  -我们要带他回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What? -We're taking him home?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们会不会太善良了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Isn't that awfully nice of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.89,0:07:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许你刚才听到的 和我听到的不是同一件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Maybe we didn't hear the same thing just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.43,0:07:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们之间发生了一些事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Something happened between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道是什么 也不知道那代表什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what it is or what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我告诉你 我听到的是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm telling you, what I heard is that if we were
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.69,0:07:48.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们把他留在里面等死 我们就会永远失去她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to leave him up there to die, we'll have lost her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远失去她 你是认真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Lost her forever? Are you being serious right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.53,0:07:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈洛德 我告诉你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Harold, I'm telling you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.20,0:07:55.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我的理解 而我不想冒这个险\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that is what I heard and I'm not willing to risk it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.62,0:07:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 没错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.54,0:07:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要带他回家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we're taking him home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.42,0:08:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天啊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.04,0:08:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很怕她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're terrified of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.42,0:08:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你本来很肯定她死了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You were so sure she was dead. Was it because
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.84,0:08:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-是因为她没死会更可怕吗  -不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-the alternative is even scarier? -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.73,0:08:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一个来找他的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are not the first to come for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.02,0:08:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是第一个看到机会的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not the first to see a moment where there seems to be an opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当他看起来很虚弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where he seems weakened…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assure you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.03,0:08:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只是外表看来如此而已\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he only seems that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你没什么好说的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have nothing to say to you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的耐心快被磨光了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}my patience is wearing thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.42,0:08:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果他在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If he were here…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会比我更凶狠\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he would be far less understanding than I…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.17,0:08:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.38,0:08:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有自认为有的影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you had the leverage you seem to think you do…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在早就被叫回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have been recalled by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就会被逮捕了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I would have been arrested.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.97,0:10:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来要说英语\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}English then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.39,0:10:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是情报官员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're an intelligence officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会说手下听不懂的语言吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You speak something your men won't understand, no?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很高兴你问了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm very glad you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这表示你根本不知道自己惹上了什么麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It means you have no idea what you just stumbled into.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道法拉兹哈姆札的生意 对喀布尔有多重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No idea how important Faraz Hamzad's commerce is to Kabul.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.62,0:10:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道我在其中扮演的角色\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No idea the role I play in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你惹了多大的麻烦\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No idea how much trouble you are in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.87,0:10:46.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,政府很担心因为我们上次的转账延误了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Ministry was concerned because our last transfer was delayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们受到的制裁很复杂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The sanctions you are under are complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.30,0:10:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们尽力绕过制裁 但出了点差错\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We are doing the best we can to stay ahead of them, but we stumbled.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以政府允许你来这里骚扰我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Ministry allowed you to come up here to harass us because of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.18,0:11:05.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这会让他们知道没什么好担心的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but this will assure them there is nothing to be concerned about.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:11.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们利用你来传达信息给我们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They used you to send a message to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这笔钱就是我的回复\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This money is my reply.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就此结束\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the matter is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里再做什么 你就得负责\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Anything more you do from here, you will answer for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.12,0:11:23.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我保证\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.04,0:11:30.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.65,0:11:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哪来的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Where did you get this money?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.11,0:11:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会想知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't wanna know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.61,0:11:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈 我们现在有更大的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Mother, we have bigger problems than that right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.49,0:12:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有比这更严重的问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What could be bigger problems than this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.16,0:12:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听说过摩根伯特这个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you ever heard of a man named Morgan Bote?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是把丹切斯交出来的幕后主使\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He is the one who was behind the deal to deliver Dan Chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们反而抓走帕瓦娜 看来因此而生气的人就是他\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And it would seem he is the one who was so angry we took Parwana instead,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他冻结了我们所有的资产 想看着我们就此完蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he's frozen all our assets and means to see us ruined over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.83,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想问你一个问题\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just want to ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.46,0:13:34.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法路克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farouk! Farouk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要我儿子做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What do you want from my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法路克…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farouk…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近在这里见过新来的人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Have you seen anyone new here recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.81,0:13:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个女人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.14,0:13:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法路克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farouk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:13:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 我知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ok… I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.86,0:14:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这女人不会说我们的语言吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This woman can't speak our language, can she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.91,0:14:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道她的名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Do you know her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.37,0:14:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能告诉我她的名字吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Can you tell me her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.25,0:14:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法路克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farouk! Farouk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.46,0:14:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法路克\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Farouk! Farouk!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.05,0:15:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该把车停在隐密一点的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Probably could have parked someplace a little less public.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.55,0:15:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想问什么就问吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Ask me what you want to ask me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.90,0:16:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有一辈子的时间告诉她你的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You had a lifetime to tell her your story.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.53,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在你却担心我敢告诉她我的说法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And now you're concerned I might have had the nerve to tell her mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟她说了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What did you say to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.67,0:16:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你继续担心吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You can stay concerned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要下去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm gonna head down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.10,0:16:31.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没事 我来处理\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Oh, no, no. I'm fine. I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不认为这是个好主意 -你待在这里我会比较安心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I don't think that's a good idea. -I'd feel better if you stayed back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.26,0:17:04.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好了 听着 -不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-All right, listen. -No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.63,0:17:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又不知道我要说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't even know what I'm gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.18,0:17:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我现在没办法思考 开头是「听着」的话\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know that if it starts with, "Listen," I can't deal with it right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吗 我知道你在想什么 我们太…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Okay? I know what's going on in your head. We're way too--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样 我们太怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What? We're way too what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本来要说我们太像了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I was gonna say we're way too alike.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道我现在是怎么了 好吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't know what's happening to me right now, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我希望你能了解 -我了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-I need you to understand that. -I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不 你不了解 -我了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-No, you don't. -I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你无法了解\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. You can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但带他回去对我来说很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But getting him home, that's important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在我需要你也觉得这件事很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And I need it to be important to you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.18,0:17:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.22,0:17:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在我后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Stay behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.64,0:17:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道自己在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I know what I'm doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:56.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你当然知道 反正我要你待在我后面\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Of course you do. I want you to stay behind me anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这件事对我来说很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That's important to me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特种部队的直升机\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}A special forces chopper?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.32,0:18:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有个同事对塔什干很有影响力\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I have an associate who has influence with Tashkent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会进入阿富汗领空前往你指定的地点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They will enter Afghan airspace, proceed to a location you designate
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接三位乘客后过边界回来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to collect three passengers, and return back across the border.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法想象你和你同事要付出多大的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I can't imagine how much that cost you with your associate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对比你欠我的更多\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}More than what it will cost you with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.42,0:18:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说过我没有能力给你任何你想要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I told you I'm in no position to offer you anything you would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.64,0:18:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也没有了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.18,0:18:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只欠我一顿晚餐\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Dinner is what you'll owe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.69,0:18:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 不管你认为我这次欠你什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Listen, whatever it actually is you imagine I'm into you for for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.73,0:18:44.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我向你保证绝对办不到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I assure you, you can forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.90,0:18:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直升机不会在非必要的情况下\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The chopper will not want to be inside Afghan airspace
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.32,0:18:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在阿富汗领空\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}any longer than necessary,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.61,0:18:51.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也完全不想被发现\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and they will not want to be noticed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.12,0:18:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托尽量不要引起国际事件\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Try not to cause an international incident. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.67,0:19:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也许仍能活下来\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You might yet still survive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.97,0:19:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不欠法拉兹哈姆札\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You owe nothing to Faraz Hamzad…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:17.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的罪行害你们成为目标\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}who has made you all a target through his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.52,0:19:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,选择权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The choice…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你们手中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}belongs to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.86,0:19:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们直接打给部长呢\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What if we were to call the minister directly?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.91,0:19:34.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们对他的士兵开火\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We fired on his soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.62,0:19:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕现在打电话也没用了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I fear we are past phone calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:42.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有开火 这个叫摩根伯特的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And even if we hadn't, this man, Morgan Bote,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.13,0:19:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知怎么地冻结了一切\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}he has somehow managed to freeze everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.92,0:19:48.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国账户 海外账户\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The US accounts, the offshore accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.51,0:19:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的钱和承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our money and the promise of more of it
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等梅西巴哈矿床全面运作后 会给他们更多的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}once the Meshbahar Deposit is fully operational
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.26,0:19:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是塔利班不敢轻举妄动的原因\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}were what held the Taliban at bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.89,0:19:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没有钱 我们就毫无防备\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But without it, we are defenseless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.52,0:20:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来可以有更好的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There had to have been a better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.73,0:20:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你当初问我 我就会帮忙找到更好的方法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you would have asked me, I would have helped to find a better way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.03,0:20:11.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我告诉你 如果我们之中\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I promise, if one of the two of us should be angry
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人该为这件事处理不当而生气\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}about how this was mishandled,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会是你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}it isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.42,0:20:26.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在她安全抵达前\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He didn't want anyone to know…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.30,0:20:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不想让任何人知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}until she was here safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.13,0:20:36.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂 真的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I get it. I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是要付出的代价\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But the cost of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.35,0:20:42.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们到现在还不知道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}we are only beginning to know what it'll be.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.29,0:21:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:03.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待命\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}standing by…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听到了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.22,0:22:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回到你的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Report back to your position, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.10,0:22:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请回到你的位置\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Report back to your position, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.44,0:22:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是没有回应\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Still no response…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.78,0:22:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道他最后的位置吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}do we have his last position?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.28,0:22:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再确认一次\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Check again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.49,0:22:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I am here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你在这里为自己说话…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Perhaps if you'd been here instead to speak for yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.18,0:23:14.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许事情就不会如此失控\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}things wouldn't have gotten so out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.80,0:23:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就说得简单一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Let me make this simple for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.22,0:23:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己现身\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Show yourself here…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.48,0:23:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会亲自带你去喀布尔政府\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and I will take you to the Ministry in Kabul myself…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.69,0:23:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时你可以解释那个美国女人是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}where you can explain who the American woman is…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.78,0:23:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为何两个美国人想独自拯救她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}why two Americans tried to rescue her alone…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.40,0:23:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有他们为何应该信任你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and why they should be expected to trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.24,0:23:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点决定\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Decide quickly…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.45,0:23:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,否则情况只会更严重\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or things here will only get uglier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们得走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We must go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-去喀布尔  -对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-To Kabul? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.58,0:23:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你来说不安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That can't be safe for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.00,0:23:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.59,0:23:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么样不重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not important what happens to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.34,0:23:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是我们的人民安全\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What matters is that our people are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:57.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我们得走了 -她说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-We must go. -She's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:24:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你这样回去 他会杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you go back there like this, he's gonna kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.60,0:24:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后拿走他想要的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and then he's gonna take whatever he wants anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你算老几\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.40,0:24:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭什么认为你有资格说\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you to have an opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.57,0:24:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎样对我和我的人民最好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}of what is best for me and the people I lead?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.82,0:24:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭什么认为我该听你的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you that I should account for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.29,0:24:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你问了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And since you're asking,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.83,0:24:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是竭尽全力确保\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm the guy who's going out of his way
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.58,0:24:27.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会在回家的路上摔下马死掉的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to make sure you don't fall off your horse and die on your way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.75,0:24:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你以为这样就能让我对你有好感\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And if you think that earns you a position with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.25,0:24:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偿还你以为能偿还的债务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that services a debt you imagine might be repaid,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.63,0:24:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就大错特错了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}you are terribly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.31,0:24:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-如果我跟你一起去呢  -什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-What if I went with you? -What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.27,0:24:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你一起进村子里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}All the way into the village with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.35,0:24:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你为什么要做这种事  -这样我才能化解这件事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-Why on Earth would you do that? -So I can diffuse all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.90,0:24:48.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要怎么做\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How on Earth would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.90,0:24:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-说实话 -艾蜜莉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-With the truth. -Emily.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.82,0:24:54.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无线电里的人想知道 你为什么绑架联邦调查局探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The man on the radio wants to know why you kidnapped an FBI agent.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.36,0:24:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这里没有联邦调查局探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But there is no FBI agent here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.07,0:24:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安琪拉亚当斯已经不存在了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There is no Angela Adams anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.03,0:25:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了这么多事 她怎么可能还存在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I mean, how could there be after all of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.12,0:25:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实是 我在这里出生 然后被带走\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The truth is, I was born here and I was taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.04,0:25:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是家族事务\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is a family story.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.92,0:25:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对你不会造成任何伤害\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Nothing that could possibly be compromising to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.17,0:25:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不行 -为什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- No. No. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.30,0:25:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔利班的秘密警察可不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The Taliban's secret police are not exactly known
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.80,0:25:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会听别人讲道理的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}for their readiness to listen to reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.14,0:25:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在乎他喜不喜欢 他只需要担心…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't care if he likes it. He just needs to worry that…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.06,0:25:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他手上的牌比他想的更弱\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that he has a weaker hand than the one he thought he was holding.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.89,0:25:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会杀了你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He'd kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.15,0:25:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是我造成的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I did this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.20,0:25:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打开这扇门\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I opened this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.95,0:25:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成的危险…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And the danger that has resulted--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会降临在你身上\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It will not fall upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.63,0:25:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会允许的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not permit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.80,0:26:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你警告过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You warned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.17,0:26:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.34,0:26:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「安琪拉亚当斯已经不存在了」\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"There's no Angela Adams anymore."
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.22,0:26:45.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你警告过我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You warned me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.93,0:26:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果在那个时候\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}That if I wasn't careful with her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.06,0:26:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有小心应对她\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}in that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.98,0:26:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她就会离开我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}then she'd disappear on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.69,0:26:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到会在同一天早上发生\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I didn't imagine it would happen the same morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.94,0:26:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想她不是那个意思\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}No. I don't think she meant it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.32,0:27:00.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想她不是在说你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I don't think that was about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.07,0:27:02.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是和我有关\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It was a little about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.28,0:27:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我横跨半个地球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I just came halfway around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.58,0:27:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就为了拯救一个不想再存在的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to save a person who doesn't want to exist anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.79,0:27:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果早知道这样 你就会不来吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you have done anything different if you had known that?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.33,0:27:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个混蛋 当然不是\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're such an asshole. Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.75,0:27:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不喜欢那种感觉\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}But I'm not thrilled about how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.67,0:27:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我想跟你谈… -天啊 好吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}-And I'm trying to talk to you about-- -Jesus, fine. Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.55,0:27:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我警告你的时候 你就该听我的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You should have listened to me when I warned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.10,0:27:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样好一点了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Better?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.02,0:27:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事她又没有发言权\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not like she had a say in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.06,0:27:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是说发生这件事后 安琪拉亚当斯星期一还会再去上班\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It's not like Angela Adams is gonna show up again for work on Monday after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.61,0:27:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以为也许会有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I guess I thought there might be a way
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.70,0:27:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以保住这个名字\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that we would fight to save the name
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.08,0:27:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以某种办法做到\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}somehow,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.16,0:27:50.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这对我们两个都很重要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}since it was so important to both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.37,0:27:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想我是该生气 但那孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I suppose I should be angry, but that kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.79,0:27:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她绕了大半个地球\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she came halfway around the world
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.88,0:28:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寻找没人愿意给她的解答\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}to find answers that no one else would give her,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.42,0:28:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让她能面对真相\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}so she could stare the truth in the eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.97,0:28:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而当我试图利用阶级\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}And in the moment when I tried to pull rank
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.51,0:28:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她感到内疚\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and make her feel guilty about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.35,0:28:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她却死盯着我 叫我去死\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}she stared me dead in the eyes and told me to go fuck myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.77,0:28:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你至少得稍微以她为荣吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How could you not be at least a little proud of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.65,0:28:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爱怎么说你都行\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He can say what he wants about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.24,0:28:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你教出了一个了不起的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You raised a hell of a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.31,0:28:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口被封住了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The entrance is sealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.44,0:28:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前门进不去\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}There's no way in the front door.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.27,0:29:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你必须从… -不\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}- You're gonna have to go-- - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.36,0:29:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要从密道\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will not steal into my own home
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.53,0:29:08.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,溜回自己家\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}through secret doors.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.41,0:29:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要面对他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I will face them where they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.46,0:29:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.25,0:29:20.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很遗憾事情变成这样\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm sorry it was this way,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.84,0:29:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不后悔\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}but I'm not sorry
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.01,0:29:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你看到这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}that now you have seen this place,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.13,0:29:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有让这地方也看到你\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}and it has seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.23,0:29:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们会杀了他吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They're gonna kill him, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.36,0:29:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的直升机很快就会到了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Our ride is gonna be getting here awful soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.08,0:29:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我们要离开这里\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If we're gonna get out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.83,0:29:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得告诉他们要在哪里碰头\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I gotta let them know where we're gonna meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.12,0:30:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 你该打电话给他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah. You should call 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.47,0:30:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来不用这样的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}It didn't have to be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.35,0:30:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你大可以让事情简单一点\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You could've made this so much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.56,0:31:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要跟我走…\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Are you coming with me…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.77,0:31:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是我们得被迫做你们的人没完成的事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}or will we be forced to finish what your people started?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.17,0:31:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们不会在这里降落\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}They won't set down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.59,0:31:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里太多活动了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not with all the activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.68,0:31:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要翻过这个山脊\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}We'll hump over the ridge here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.72,0:31:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们有多少时间\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}How much time we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.89,0:31:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不多了 他们不会等太久的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Not much. They won't wait long.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.65,0:31:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾蜜莉 不要\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Emily. Emily! Emily, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.57,0:31:53.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 计划有变 我们得改变路线 就是现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, change of plans. We need to redirect. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.42,0:32:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.80,0:33:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我你是谁吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Would you like to tell me who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.19,0:33:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别担心他们\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Don't worry about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.36,0:33:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下他就要跟我一起走了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}In a few moments, he will be coming with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.28,0:33:18.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不会为了阻止这件事而害死所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}He won't get everyone killed to prevent this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.78,0:33:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 现在\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}So, at this point,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.08,0:33:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这只是出于我个人的好奇心\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}this is just for the sake of my own curiosity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.92,0:33:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个被绑架的美国人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You are the abducted American.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.04,0:33:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造成这一切混乱的人\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}The one who started all of this mess.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.51,0:33:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.81,0:33:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是联邦调查局的探员\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You're an agent with the FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.11,0:33:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是真的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This is also true?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.74,0:33:59.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你告诉我 或许会有帮助\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}If you tell me, it might help.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.78,0:34:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也许会愿意大事化小\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I might be willing to make this just a little easier on everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.87,0:34:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我不用每天睡觉前 都还在想我不知道什么事\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}if I didn't have to end the day still wondering what it is I'm missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.17,0:34:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不属于这个地方\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}You don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.30,0:34:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是你的战争\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}This doesn't need to be your fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.59,0:34:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Just tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.89,0:34:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.54,0:35:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字是帕瓦娜哈姆札\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}My name is Parwana Hamzad.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.95,0:35:31.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「是谁授权的 」是我授权的\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}"On whose authority?" On my authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.46,0:35:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 但如果我们死了你就无法撤离我们了\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Yeah, but you can't evac us if we're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.83,0:35:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事我也有责任 照做就对了 明白吗\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}I'm on the hook for this. Just do it! You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.96,0:35:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂\N{\fn微软雅黑\fs14}Hello?

